{"tid":583581,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"郵差涉街頭非禮人妻   事主感到被人掐屁股","createTime":"2018-03-07T06:11:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-07T06:54:26.000Z","uid":48093,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"96f1b8dbb53377f58ef0e4b1e176f8f35fb86b39","tid":583581,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T06:11:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180307/large/1520402737_1d6e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180307%2Flarge%2F1520402737_1d6e.jpg&h=db77b188&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n從台灣嫁來香港、於英國取得碩士學歷的人妻，去年8月與丈夫一前一後的逛旺角通菜街時，稱感到遭人掐屁股，轉身望到一男子站在她的後方，她通知丈夫後，丈夫將對方捉住報警。<br />\n<br />\n報稱任郵差的男子毛獻輝（56歲）被控非禮罪，案件今在裁判法院開審。事主今供稱，去年8月13下午近6時，她與丈夫在旺角通菜街用膳完畢後，兩人一前一後逛街。事主稱當時街上人流少，不算迫。<br />\n當時她穿著薄身及膝濶身褲，突然「感覺有人掐左邊屁股」約一秒，「不是包包碰到，明顯感覺到被掐」。事主轉頭便望到被告背著她在她左後方，周圍並沒有其他人，她「嚇了一大跳」即告訴丈夫，丈夫也感到很驚訝，跑去捉住被告，被告說「沒有、沒有」。<br />\n而當事主丈夫隨後準備宣誓作供時，被告突然指當日捉住他的男人「大隻好多」。被告表現激動，用手指着裁判官聲稱要跟裁判官直接說話，遭裁判官批評無禮貌，審訊一度暫停。"},{"pid":"9521d92d22299cee1598b53efcd37411b08a51c2","tid":583581,"uid":174110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T06:17:06.000Z","msg":"台灣女人果然夠曬敏感<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n感到被人掐屁股<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港得一分<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f79a986521b0b2cdeba2d88ebf703c68dbfdb37","tid":583581,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T06:29:56.000Z","msg":"有咩誤會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45a7055068d8d76eb33da832b6de216bfa790b38","tid":583581,"uid":25635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T06:31:32.000Z","msg":"非禮???<br />\n你應該嗌搶野...搶野係衰佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"551c997bee8757597da27f0f8e5f9df4ff8bad84","tid":583581,"uid":7814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T06:36:33.000Z","msg":"係掐都唔係掐呢d 老閪啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37da6c798de0fe86a14a74600a496bb6bbebad83","tid":583581,"uid":91771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"551c997bee8757597da27f0f8e5f9df4ff8bad84","tid":583581,"uid":7814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T06:36:33.000Z","msg":"係掐都唔係掐呢d 老閪啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T06:54:26.000Z","msg":"老閪都搣返吓先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都係肉"}]}